<i>the American dream.</i>

34
00:01:47.407 --> 00:01:49.209
<i>I live</i>
<i>in a beautiful neighborhood.</i>

35
00:01:49.242 --> 00:01:50.712
<i>I own a beautiful home.</i>

36
00:01:50.745 --> 00:01:56.350
