49
00:02:23.077 --> 00:02:24.579
-I don't know.
-Yes. I am.

50
00:02:24.612 --> 00:02:26.179
NATE: <i>And she's great</i>
<i>at details.</i>

51
00:02:26.213 --> 00:02:28.116
<i>Our whole world is run from</i>

52
00:02:28.148 --> 00:02:30.384
