<i>she made.</i>

53
00:02:30.417 --> 00:02:32.352
<i>I don't always know</i>
<i>what the colors mean.</i>

54
00:02:32.386 --> 00:02:34.656
<i>but I'm not the one. you know.</i>
<i>who picks up the kids.</i>

55
00:02:34.689 --> 00:02:37.725
<i>so I kind of don't have to.</i>
<i>I guess.</i>

56
00:02:38.258 --> 00:02:39.694
