-[KATIE CHUCKLES]

61
00:02:45.700 --> 00:02:47.902
NATE: <i>But it's not like Katie</i>
<i>does everything by herself.</i>

62
00:02:47.935 --> 00:02:49.070
<i>I help.</i>

63
00:02:49.103 --> 00:02:50.872
